external_knowledge:
- "wanderers through the digital forest" metaphorically refers to users who explore technology companies;
- "trees of innovation" metaphorically refers to technology companies, symbolizing growth and advancements;
- "cherished on the digital frontier" means the companies are in the user's list of favorite companies;
- "value their roots held in the soil of the market" metaphorically refers to the closing prices of the company stocks, representing their market value.

sql:
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM data_providers
WHERE status = 'active';

SELECT data_provider_id, MAX(last_sync_date) AS last_sync_date
FROM data_providers
GROUP BY data_provider_id;

SELECT DISTINCT c.company_name
FROM companies c
JOIN favorite_companies fc ON c.company_id = fc.company_id;
